<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.5.6">
<l>mēlum vaṉpaḻi naṅkuṭikkiva ḷeṉṟaṉṉai kāṇakkoṭāḷ.</l>
<l>cōlaicūḻ taṇṭiruk kuṟuṅkuṭi nampiyai nāṉkaṇṭapiṉ</l>
<l>kōlanīḷ koṭimūkkun tāmaraik kaṇṇuṅ kaṉivāyu</l>
<l>nīlamēṉiyu nāṉku tōḷumeṉ ṉeñca niṟaintaṉavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“Forthwith she [is] strong blame to our familiy”, so mother doesn’t let [me be] seen.</l>
<l>After I saw Nampi of cool Tirukkuṟuṅkuṭi surrounded by groves,</l>
<l>the beautiful long nose and the lotus eyes and the fruit mouth</l>
<l>and the blue body and the four arms have filled my heart.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
